{"tid":363973,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"係地鐵見到廢老真係忍唔住…","createTime":"2017-08-18T04:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T06:16:18.000Z","uid":5843,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6e0f59489c305b33a1121562779a6fe874a7ed8c","tid":363973,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T04:20:30.000Z","msg":"啱啱金鐘轉線過海去旺角買啲嘢<br />\n一開門見到得返一個位，個廢老已經批掙想爬我頭<br />\n本身都唔攰，見佢咁想坐即刻一個箭步行衝去個位度，再另轉身慢慢放底個袋<br />\n見住佢死死氣去第二卡搵位真係忍唔住ke一聲笑出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03a1b28a9d569c4081b72a52dad2228a3f52764d","tid":363973,"uid":57549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T04:24:34.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1333a56e6e366cf5d476a40af7975bc387df5e1","tid":363973,"uid":42586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T04:30:59.000Z","msg":"清好波"},{"pid":"fae6dd245a753cb8dfd8c14e45cb508556782d76","tid":363973,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T04:32:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大家略盡綿力 齊齊爭櫈仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11afc01005becaa5a95fa43b0b941d7ec2ef414f","tid":363973,"uid":42044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T04:37:10.000Z","msg":"做得好"},{"pid":"869fc4a3ead7c1b77fd3ad2082f83cf641213185","tid":363973,"uid":42044,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T04:41:17.000Z","msg":"本身排第一等巴士，已經見倒個阿婆隊頭嘅外圍準備打尖。我第一腳踏上巴士，個阿婆晌我左後邊攝上車，我就用左膊迫返佢落車再瞓晌馬路度，其他人睇倒佢叫救命都唔理佢， 大快人心！"},{"pid":"b2625627e074082950edfa3422a47deac297c2a5","tid":363973,"uid":2146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T04:41:57.000Z","msg":"樓主好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c08ac9ed2bc3405e57912866da22b8dc8f3f4c4c","tid":363973,"ui